{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>救援人員接報到場，發現49歲姓黃女事主昏迷不醒，被送往治理，期後被證實死亡。據了解，事主患有身體病。警方正調查事故起因，案件列作「送院時死亡」跟進。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250816/1033347733232029696875361.jpeg/E4Pod0Qnzahe5bZU22sXykAehVGNQDNvO8xESzvMREs\" alt=\"廣華醫院。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>廣華醫院。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20211023/528554182425186304345276.png/YPFSPyCFozMVIuQGu_Ino6glMIY4r7kandpG1p3aRtY\" alt=\"馬頭圍邨。（運房局圖片）\"><figcaption>馬頭圍邨。（運房局圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-26T23:39:16.711861+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":99,"images":2,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}